| comment "Dragnet [Ransomware]: dragnet-ransomware-2024-5249 — Recovery Inhibition (ransomhub)"
| comment "Status: experimental | Level: high | ID: 0ff5779f-8017-5880-a3cd-9bc91e469d26"
